==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: bú shì yī jiā rén, bú jìn yī jiā mén
===Proverb===
'''[[不]][[是]][[一]][[家]][[人]]，[[不]][[進]][[一]][[家]][[門]]'''
# If a bride were not meant to marry into a family, fate would not bring her in the door.
===Alternate forms===
[[不是一家人，不进一家门]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])
